2ba7e0b7af96d559c861c39","tid":285842,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:36:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">提早開冷氣，到了傍晚6時關掉冷氣<br />\n<br />\n關掉雪櫃2小時，但古偉牧亦明言這是一般家庭未必會做的極端方法。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n晏晝特別接日落果陣個太陽如果哂住個單位 / 冷氣機，開冷氣其實最哂電；熜左個雪櫃再開，條友腦裝屎先講得出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e837eb7780fb10a20e76bccbeed0e006c91ac6c1","tid":285842,"uid":13115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:38:44.000Z","msg":"做環保既係咪蠢成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51fd2f470cc2e8cb72d50c9d6cda3bd9f231b03c","tid":285842,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:39:45.000Z","msg":"仆街冇睇到熄雪櫃正評咗 <br />\n你試下叫24/7嘅 data center 同 server 熄一兩個鐘睇吓點? 有冇Ups同香港household電池頂到個雪櫃一兩個鐘? 又開又熄一啲都唔環保冇科學常識"},{"pid":"c56449765b0f8e098b4cc11496834aa06c18684a","tid":285842,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做環保既係咪蠢成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港環保膠好似多好多 <br />\nSmart grid 太陽能同風力發電 做 feed-in tariff / net metering 最好都想有電池方便賣電"},{"pid":"a3102ae72ab3b98328668ad6a39ca8a7d5dad509","tid":285842,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:46:08.000Z","msg":"低收費時段幾百張rx480超頻瘋狂掘礦，呢次fat fat了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d07514d76d1f512136f25a07a88e0116de6dc38","tid":285842,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:47:17.000Z","msg":"環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa966442595a90a4c9e0089d6c6d01b07c6afe34","tid":285842,"uid":51127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:49:33.000Z","msg":"無人既時候開冷氣，係浪費，絕對唔係環保。仲